                            <comment id="14079981" author="thobbs" created="Wed, 30 Jul 2014 21:10:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Should we make the check complain about any difference between &lt;tt&gt;bootstrapTokens.size()&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;DatabaseDescriptor.getNumTokens()&lt;/tt&gt;, not just 1 and not-1?  I feel like that would be better than silently ignoring config changes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I would also keep the log message about the saved tokens that are being used.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14079999" author="brandon.williams" created="Wed, 30 Jul 2014 21:22:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think that&apos;s a good idea, updated.  Didn&apos;t mean to remove that log line, so fixed that too.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
